 English version
------------------------------------------------------------------------

The quotations included in this archive are excerpts from larger works
and their reproduction is believed to constitute "fair use". This 
collection of quotation was created by Aurelien Jarno and other people 
(see the AUTHORS file), can be found on http://www.fortunes-fr.org. 
Redistribution and use in any forms, are permitted provided that the 
following conditions are met:
* the name of the authors (file AUTHORS) and the address of the original
package shall be included in all copies or substancial portions of the 
collection;
* a changelog (file CHANGES) shall be maintain in all copies or 
substancial portions of the collection.

